article.description: — Aubin Gateretse's 26 points helped Stetson defeat Milwaukee 85-67 at the Sunshine Slam on Monday.
article.headline: Gateretse scores 26 and Stetson knocks off Milwaukee 85-67 at Sunshine Slam
article.linkText: Gateretse scores 26 and Stetson knocks off Milwaukee 85-67 at Sunshine Slam
article.story: DAYTONA BEACH, Fla. -- — Aubin Gateretse's 26 points helped Stetson defeat Milwaukee 85-67 at the Sunshine Slam on Monday. Gateretse added 11 rebounds and four blocks for the Hatters (2-2). Jalen Blackmon added 22 points and Stephan D. Swenson had 11 points. The Panthers (2-3) were led in scoring by BJ Freeman, who finished with 20 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
